{"word":"G4312 - προπετής - propetḗs - prop-et-ace' - Heady","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προπετής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">propetḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">prop-et-ace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Heady</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பதறிச்செய்கிற, துணிகரமுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. falling forward, headlong, sloping, precipitous"},{"paragraph":"2. precipitate, rash, reckless"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G4098 - πίπτω - píptō - pip'-to/4098\">G4098</a>; <i>falling forward</i>, that is, <i>headlong</i> (figuratively <i>precipitate</i>): - heady, rash [-ly].</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}